text: KDKD (1280 AM) is a radio station broadcasting an Oldies format. Licensed to Clinton, Missouri, United States, the station is currently owned by Alpha Media and licensed to Alpha Media Licensee LLC. KDKD features programming from ABC Radio and Dial Global. ==References== ==External links== DKD Category:Oldies radio stations in the United States Category:Radio stations established in 1992 Category:Alpha Media radio stations
